  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Bonus Action, you can expend a use of your Channel Divinity to issue a challenge that compels other creatures to do battle with you. Each creature of your choice that you can see within 30 feet of you must make a Charisma saving throw. On a failed save, a creature cannot willingly move more than 10 feet away from you. This effect ends on the creature if you have the &amp;Reference[Incapacitated apply=false] condition, if you die, or if the creature is more than 30 feet away from you.</p>",
